# Implementation Plan - Complete SkillForge Platform

## Goal
Create a complete, fully functional social learning platform with no 404 errors, PWA support, full mobile responsiveness, and all requested features.

## This Iteration - MUST COMPLETE

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Priority 1**: Mobile Responsiveness - App must work perfectly on mobile devices like a native app.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Priority 2**: Fix all 404 errors by creating all missing pages and routes.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Required Features**: Share functionality, PWA support, Search, Notifications, Comments, DMs, Groups, Challenges, Badges.

